313
00:27:56,174 --> 00:27:57,676
[sobbing]

314
00:28:02,972 --> 00:28:03,973
[Gukho straining]

315
00:28:07,352 --> 00:28:09,813
No matter how fucked up
the world has become,

316
00:28:12,023 --> 00:28:14,651
