413
00:34:30,777 --> 00:34:31,778
[gun fires]

414
00:34:37,575 --> 00:34:38,576
[gun fires]

415
00:34:39,994 --> 00:34:40,995
[gun fires]

416
00:34:41,120 --> 00:34:44,540
