443
00:36:35,276 --> 00:36:36,277
[Gukho screams]

444
00:36:36,402 --> 00:36:37,403
[gun fires]

445
00:37:26,160 --> 00:37:27,912
Fuck, my 20 billion won!

446
00:37:31,165 --> 00:37:32,416
My money!

447
00:37:32,500 --> 00:37:34,043
