483
00:39:17,938 --> 00:39:20,274
[Suchang] <i>Yes, as of right now.</i>

484
00:39:20,358 --> 00:39:22,109
[Sanghun] <i>Is that even possible in Korea?</i>

485
00:39:22,193 --> 00:39:23,527
<i>In the 21st century?</i>

486
00:39:24,612 --> 00:39:26,364
<i>What did Gukho's son say? He saw him.</i>

487
00:39:27,740 --> 00:39:28,908
[Suchang] <i>He's keeping quiet.</i>

488
00:39:35,331 --> 00:39:36,332
Oh, right.

489
00:39:36,832 --> 00:39:38,000
