495
00:40:16,205 --> 00:40:17,206
Dad...

496
00:40:17,790 --> 00:40:18,874
Honey,

497
00:40:19,291 --> 00:40:20,626
did you hear that?

498
00:40:20,709 --> 00:40:22,253
She spoke.

499
00:40:22,336 --> 00:40:23,379
